text: Mindishevo () is a rural locality (a village) in Ishimbayevsky Selsoviet, Salavatsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 304 as of 2010. There are 6 streets. == Geography == It is located 37 km from Maloyaz, 1 km from Ishimbayevo. == References == Category:Rural localities in Salavatsky District
title: Mindishevo
